          <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 leading-snug">View curated providers, check certifications, and read real client reviews.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[22px] mx-auto mb-3">&#x1F4E9;</div>
          <h3 class="text-sm font-bold mb-1">Request Quotes</h3>
          <p class="text-[13px] text-gray-500 leading-snug">Select up to 5 providers and send your project details. Free, no obligation.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-primary-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-[22px] mx-auto mb-3">&#x2696;&#xFE0F;</div>
